<div class="flow-container" data-controller="animate">
  <%= render 'shared/progress_bar', step: 5 %>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-6">
      <%= render 'shared/chat', message: message %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row justify-content-center" data-delay="2" data-animate-target="contentContainer">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-6">
        <div class="content-container" >
          <div class="packs-wrapper mb-4">
            <div class="w-100 text-center"><%= image_tag(asset_path('components/next-step-banner/cards.png')) %></div>
            <div class="pack-card">
              <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
                <h2>Starter Pack</h2>
                <span class="price"><%= order.currency_symbol %><%= order.total_amount_display %></span>
              </div>
              <p>The best offers to get you started</p>
              <ul>
                <% order.items.each do |item| %>
                  <li>  <i class='fas fa-check'></i>  <%= item.product.name %></li>
                <% end %>
                <li ><i class="fas fa-plus invisible"></i> + free surprise üç™</li>
                <li ><i class="fas fa-plus invisible"></i> + free shipping üì¶</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="cta-wrapper">
              <%= link_to 'Buy now', new_shipping_path(order.id) %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <%= link_to 'Back', new_cart_path, class:'btn-main-white w-100 mb-5' %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-6 testimonials-packs ">
          <h2>They liked us</h2>
          <div class="testimonials-wrapper">
            <div class="testimonial d-flex align-items-start">
              <%= image_tag(asset_path('components/packs-card/testimonial-1.png'), width: 40) %>
              <div class="content">
                <div class="stars d-flex align-items-center">
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                </div>
                <p>I was excited for my trip to London but also a little scared. This pack helped me to have some basics settled early on. </p>
                <span>Shane - June 27, 2021</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial d-flex align-items-start">
              <%= image_tag(asset_path('components/packs-card/testimonial-2.png'), width: 40) %>
              <div class="content">
                <div class="stars d-flex align-items-center">
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star-half"></i>
                </div>
                <p>The pack was nice but guys, the suprise is definitely hilarious. </p>
                <span>Robert - June 19, 2021</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial d-flex align-items-start">
              <%= image_tag(asset_path('components/packs-card/testimonial-3.png'), width: 40) %>
              <div class="content">
                <div class="stars d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                  <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                </div>
                <p>I arrived with 2 suitcases in Charles de Gaulle airport. Glad I was picked-up, this would have been a nightmare otherwise. </p>
                <span class="mb-4">Vladimir - June 13, 2021</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
    <div class="coming-soon-banner" data-delay="2">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="title">Understand the pricing </p>
        <p class="subtitle"><strong>movido is 100% free!</strong> We do not charge you any fees for the offers you choose or for our service. The costs that you see are 100% transparent and reflect the actual retail prices of our partners.</p>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>

